Mtundu $1 wa MediaWiki ukukhumbika kuti mugwiliske ntchito jani ili.
Wonani [[Special:Version|mtundu wa jani]].

sort-rowspan-error: Jani lino lina thebulu ilo lina mizele inandi kujumpha unandi wa mizele ya thebulu. Munganozga ivi kwizila mwakusintha jani lino.
nosuchactiontext:
Icho mwate mupange kwizila pa adilesi ya intaneti kulije.
Mukwenela kuti mwangulemba uheni adilesi ya intaneti, panji mwangulondezga linki yambula kwenelela.
Nyengo zinyake ichi chingang'anamulaso kuti sofutiweya iyo {{SITENAME}} ikugwiliska ntchito ina suzgo.
nospecialpagetext: Mwapempha jani lapadera ilo likugwira ntchito yayi. Mndandanda wa majani ghapadera ghakuzomerezgeka ungasangika pa [[Special:SpecialPages|{{int:majani ghapadera}}]].
databaseerror-text:
Suzgo lasangika mu databezi.
Ichi chingang'anamula kuti sofutiweya ina suzgo.
databaseerror-textcl: Fumbo ilo mwangufumba lasangika na suzgo pakuzgoleka.
transaction-duration-limit-exceeded:
Kuti muleke kupanga nyengo yitali yakuwerezgawerezga, ivi mwate mupange vyalekeskeka chifukwa nyengo yakulembera yakukwana ($1) yajumpha mphaka ya sekondi $2.
Usange mukusintha vinthu vinandi nyengo yimoza, yezgani kuchita milimo yinandi yichokoyichoko m’malo mwake.
transaction-max-statement-time-exceeded:
Kuti muleke kupanga nyengo yitali yakuwerezgawerezga, ivi mwate mupange vyalekeskeka chifukwa nyengo yakulembera yajumpha mlingo.
Usange mukuŵelenga vinthu vinandi nyengo yimoza, yezgani kuchita milimo yinandi yichokoyichoko m’malo mwake.
laggedreplicamode: Chenjezgo:: Pa jani ili palije ivyo vyasintha mwasonosono apa.
enterlockreason: Ikani chifukwa cha kukiyila, kusazgapo na utali wa nyengo apo loko uzamufumilapo
readonlytext:
Pa nyengo yasono nkhokwe ya vyakulemba yajalikila ku vyakulemba viphya na vyakusintha vinyake, panji na chakulinga chakuti nkhokwe iyi ya vyakulemba inozgeke, ndipo yiŵengeso makola.

Mulaŵiliri wa pulogiramu uyo wakajala pulogilamu iyi walongosola kuti: $1
filerenameerror: Kusintha zina la "$1" kuti likhale "$2" kwatondeka.
directoryreadonlyerror: "$1" ni malo ghakuti mungachita kuŵazga kwekha.
badarticleerror: Ichi mwate muchite chingapangika yayi pa jani ili.
cannotdelete: Jani panji fayilo ya "$1" yakatondeka kusisimwika. Panji munthu munyake ndiyo wali kusisimwa kale.
delete-scheduled:
Jani la "$1" lasankhika kuti lifufutikenge mwakuyana na nyengo iyo yathyeka.
Chonde fwasani.
delete-hook-aborted:
Kufufuta kwadumulika na sofutiweya.
Palije kulongosola uko kwapasika.
no-null-revision: Kupanga mbili ya kuwelezga kwa jani la "$1" kwatondeka
badtitletext:
Zina la ichi mwapempha palije,panji ntchakusokonekela na viyowoyelo vinyake.
Panji china malemba ghambula kuzomelezgeka mu mitu.
title-invalid: Mutu wa jani ilo mwapempha ngwambura kwenelera
title-invalid-empty: Mutu wa jani ilo mwapempha ulije kanthu panji uli na chiyambi cha zina chekha.
title-invalid-utf8: Mutu wa jani ilo lapempheka uli na ndondomeko ya UTF-8 yambura kugwira ntchito.
title-invalid-interwiki: Mutu wa jani ilo lapempheka uli na ulalo wa malemba ghakugaska agho ghangagwiliskika ntchito pakulemba miti yayi.
title-invalid-talk-namespace: Mutu wa jani ilo mukupempha nda jani lakuchezgelapo ilo lakuti lingaŵapo yayi.
title-invalid-characters: Mutu wa jani ilo lapempheka uli na malemba ghambula ghambula kuzomelezgeka ngati ni agha: "$1".
title-invalid-relative: Mutu uli na nthowa yakulongozgera. Mazina gha jani (./, ../) ngambura kuzomelezgeka, chifukwa kanandi ghangasangika yayi pala ghagwiliskika ntchito na nkhonthi ya mgwiliski.
title-invalid-magic-tilde: Mutu wa jani ilo mwapempha uli na malemba ghakuoneka ngati ni majigha (<nowiki>~~~</nowiki>).

exception-nologin-text: Chonde njilani mu akaunti kuti musinthe panji kuchita icho mwate muchite.
cannotlogoutnow-text: Kufuma mu akaunti nkhwamachitiko yayi pala mukugwiliska ntchito $1.
welcomecreation-msg:
Akaunti yinu yapangika.
Mungasintha vyakukhwaskana akaunti yinu pa{{SITENAME}} [[Special:Preferences|vyakunozga]] pala mwakhumba.
cannotcreateaccount-text: Kupanga akaunti mwakudumula kulije pa wiki iyi.
password-change-forbidden: Mungasintha yayi ma pasiwedi pa wiki iyi.
externaldberror: Panguŵa suzgo la pakupokela zgolo panji ndimwe ŵakuzomelezgeka yayi kusintha akaunti yinu ya kuwalo.
createacct-reason: Chifukwa (apo muli kale mu akaunti inyake)
createacct-reason-help: Uthenga walongosoreka mu mndandanda wakupangila akaunti
createacct-reason-confirm: Chifukwa icho mukaika chikaŵa adilesi ya imelu. Usange ndivyo mukukhumba, chonde dofyaniso pa "pangani akaunti"
usernameinprogress: Pali kale ndondomeko ya kupanga akaunti ya zina ili. Chonde lindizgani.
userexists: Zina ili mwanjizga apa lina kale munthu. Chonde sankhani zina linyake.
createacct-normalization: Zina linu lizamusinthika kukhala "$2" chifukwa cha masuzgo gha pa kompyuta ghakukanizga.
userlogin-authpopup-closeme: Usange mwawona uthenga uwu, mungajara windo ili.
nouserspecified: Mukwenera kulemba zina la kugwiliska ntchito.
login-userblocked: Mgwiliski uyu wakanizgika. Kunjila mu akaunti nkhwakuzomelezgeka yayi.
resetpass_announce: Kuti mumalizge kujura, mukwenela kuŵika pasiwedi yiphya.
changepassword-throttled:
Mwayezga chomene kunjira sonosono apa.
Chonde lindilirani $1 pambere mundayezgeso.
anoneditwarning: Chenjezgo: Mundanjile mu akaunti yinu. Pala mulembenge chilichose IP adilesi yinu waliyose waionenge. Pala [$1 mwanjila] mu akaunti yinu panji [$2 mwapanga akaunti], vyakulemba vinu vyose viŵenge mu zina linu, na uwemi unyake.
blockedtext: Zina linu panji IP address yakanizgika. {{int:blockedtext-made-by|$1}} {{int:blockedtext-reason-comment|$2}} *{{int:blockedtext-start-time|$8}} *{{int:blockedtext-expiration-time|$6}} *{{int:blockedtext-intended-blockee|$7}} {{int:blockedtext-contact-blocker-admin|$1}} Mungagwiliska "{{int:emailuser}}" pala muna email address yinu yojuliskila [[Special:Preferences|preferences]] ndipo njakuti mungaseŵezeska. {{int:blockedtext-block-ip|$3}} {{int:blockedtext-block-id|$5}} {{int:blockedtext-include-details-queries}}
newarticletext: Mwalondezga link iyo peji lake palije dankha. Kuti mulilembe, yambani kulemba mu box pasi apa (onani [$1 peji laovwili] mwa vinandi). Pala mwizapo mwangozi, dofyani batani la browser winu back.
anontalkpagetext: ---- Ili ni jani lakudumbiskilanapo la munthu wambura kumanyikwa uyo wandapange akaunti, panji uyo wakuyigwiliska ntchito akaunti yayi. Ntheura tikwenera kugwiliskira ntchito adiresi ya IP ya nambala kuti tiŵamanye. Adiresi ya IP yanthena iyi yingagaŵika na ŵanthu ŵanandi. Usange ndimwe munthu wambura kumanyikwa uyo ivi valembeka apa vikumukhwaskani yayi, chonde [[Special:CreateAccount|pangani akaunti]] panji [[Special:UserLogin|njirani]] kuti muleke kusokonezgeka na ŵanyakhe awo ŵakuseŵezeska ntchito kwambura kumanyikwa.
noarticletext: Palije dankha mazgo pa jani lino. Munga [[Special:Search/{{PAGENAME}}|penja jani lino]] mu viyowoyelo vinyake, [{{fullurl:{{#Special:Log}}|page={{FULLPAGENAMEE}}}} penja mu ma log nghakupokelelapo], panji[{{fullurl:{{FULLPAGENAME}}|action=edit}} yatani jani lino].
noarticletext-nopermission: Pasono palije dankha mazgo ghalighose pa jani lino. Munga [[Special:Search/{{PAGENAME}}|penja mutu uwo]] mu majani ghanyake, panji [{{fullurl:{{#Special:Log}}|page={{FULLPAGENAMEE}}}} mungapenja mu mathala ghanyake], kwene mulije chilolezo chakuyata jani lino.
userpage-userdoesnotexist-view: Akaunti ya mgwiliski "$1" indalembeske pa wiki yino.
previewnote: Kumbukilani kuti ichi ntchiyelezgelo waka. Mundazomelezge dankha kusintha!
hiddencategories: Jani ili ni ndimoza mwa majani {{PLURAL:$1|mtundu wakubisika|$1 mitundu yakubisika}}:
recreate-moveddeleted-warn: Chenjezgo: Mukupangaso jani ilo lilikufufutika. Mukwenera kughanaghanirapo usange ntchakwenelera kulutilira kulemba jani ili. Mbili ya kusisimwika na kusamuskika kwa jani ili vyapelekeka pano kuti viŵe vyambura kusuzga kulondezga:
moveddeleted-notice:
Jani ili likusangika yayi.
Kufufutika, kutchinjilizika, na kuthyeka kwa jani ili kuli pasi apa.
undo-failure: Kulemba kwakana kuti kuwezgeleke mumanyuma chifukwa cha kusintha kwasono sono uko kwachitika.
histlegend:
Kupambana kwake: Sankhani mabatani gha pa wayilesi gha ivyo mwasintha kuti muyaniske na kudofya batani lakuzomelezga panji batani ilo lili pasi.
Chimanyisko: ({{int:sono}}) = mphambano na kusintha kwasonosono, ({{int:chaumalilo}}) = mphambano na kusintha kwakumanyuma, {{int:minoreditletter}} = kusintha kuchoko.

Chinthu ichi ntchaku $1 ndipo chingagwiliskikaso kunyake.
Vakulongosola vake [$2 file description page] vili pasi apa.
prefixindex: Majani ghose gha mazgu ghakudumura kukwamba
alllogstext:
Vyakuoneska vyakusazga vya mindandanda yose ya {{SITENAME}}.
Mungachepeskako kuwona mwa kusankha mtundu wa vikhongwani, zina la wakugwiliskira ntchito (kuŵika vilembo vikulu na vidoko mwatcheru), panji jani ilo lakhwaskika (kuŵikaso vilembo vikulu na vidoko mwatcheru).
watchlist-details: {{PLURAL:$1| $1 jani ili mukulilondezga| $1 majani agha mukughalondezga}} (pamoza na majani ghakuchezgelapo).
wlheader-showupdated: Majani agho ghasinthika kufuma apo mukaghawonela ghakulongosoreka mu mtundu ukulu ufipa.
wlnote: Pasi apa pali{{PLURAL:$1| kusintha kwa umalilo|vyakusintha $1 vyaumalilo}} mu nyengo yakukwana {{PLURAL:$2| ola limoza| $2 maora}}, kufuma pa $3, $4.
nocontribs: Palije chinthu icho chasangikapo chakuyana na icho mukupenja.
sp-contributions-toponly: woneska vyakulemba ivyo ni mbili iphya
metadata-help:
Chinthu ichi china vyakulemba vinyake ivo panji vikasazgika pa siku ilo kamela ikajambulilanga, panji apo makina gha ghakulemba ghakajambulila.
Pala chinthu chakwamba chasinthika, vyakulemba vinandi vikuukako.
watchlisttools-edit: Kuona na kusintha mndandanda wa ivyo mukulondezga
blockedtext-include-details-queries: Chonde sazgani vose ivo vili pachanya pakufumba ovwili.
